<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>

 https://maven.apache.org/xsd/maven-4.0.0.xsd">

			<scope>test</scope>
		</dependency>
	</dependencies>

	<build>
		<plugins>
			<plugin>
				<groupId>org.springframework.boot</groupId>

</project>
